Package com.mygames

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    This is the main driving class.
    Colorify
    This is the class to set up colors for different print statements.
    ComputerPlayer
    Computer Player class that is inherited from Player Base class.
    Game
    Provides the Game class which is the main class of the application reponsible for initializing everything required for the game like Players and Board.
    GameBoard
    This is the class which initializes the Game Board with specified size and creates an empty board to play.
    HumanPlayer
    HumanPlayer Class which is inherited from Player Base class and implements the abstract functions in addition to its own functionality.
    HumanPlayerSimulation
    Class to return a predefined set of moves to the game.
    InputParser
    InputParser class to read the contents of json file, and provide methods to initialize the player and get information from json file.
    Move
    Class Move to operate on the moves entered.
    Player
    Abstract class of Player which has an abstract method getNextMove.
